	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002325_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Burnbank Road</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hamilton</placeName> 2<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">d</hi></hi> June </p>
<lb/><p>1865. </p>
<lb/><p>Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Tidman</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>D<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> J. C. Meller</persName>
<lb/>who was surgeon 
<lb/>of the Pioneer while 
<lb/>that vessel was 
<lb/>under my charge, 
<lb/>is going out to 
<lb/><placeName>Madagascar</placeName> on 
<lb/>the 8<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> current, 
<lb/>as Consul in 
<lb/>that Island. 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002325_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>He has been there 
<lb/>for a short time 
<lb/>and saw <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Ellis</persName>
<lb/>at the capital. 
<lb/>He always behaved 
<lb/>in a very kind 
<lb/>way to the 
<w>Mission-<lb break="no"/>aries</w> under <persName>bishop 
<lb/>Mackenzie,</persName> and 
<lb/>I think would be 
<lb/>disposed to treat 
<lb/>your missionaries 
<lb/>in <placeName>Madagascar</placeName>
<lb/>in the same way. </p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002325_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/><p>If you would like 
<lb/>to call upon him 
<lb/>his address is </p>
<lb/><p><placeName>48 Queen Anne St.</placeName></p>
<lb/><p><placeName>Cavendish Square</placeName></p>
<lb/><p>and it might dispose 
<lb/>him to regard your 
<lb/>friends there with 
<lb/>favour in case 
<lb/>of their requiring 
<lb/>his medical or 
<lb/>other services. 
<lb/>As he has some 
<lb/>little respect for 
<lb/>me as his old 
<lb/>chief, I have ventured 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002325_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'-->
<lb/>to recommend him 
<lb/>to take the same kind 
<lb/>interest into <placeName><w>Mada-<lb break="no"/>gascar,</w></placeName> as he did 
<lb/>in the <placeName>Shire</placeName><w>mission-<lb break="no"/>aries,</w> and I said 
<lb/>that I would mention 
<lb/>his going out to 
<lb/>you<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">Ever yours </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
